  "remarks": "Founder and leader of the Rajah Solaiman Movement (QDe.128) and linked to\nthe Abu Sayyaf Group (QDe.001). In detention in the Philippines as of May 2011. Review\npursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 13 May\n2010. Photos included in\nReview pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
